  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yeah, all of a sudden, they say, every-- every Jew has to go to the police station and just register-- nothing else.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, you know, you always obey the law in France, you-- so we all went.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If we have known-- [LAUGHS].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We all went and put our name.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then, after this, let's see, the next-- the next thing was-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the government.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, the French, not the German.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- the-- the-- the-- the French followed the-- the French law when they ask.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I-- I really don't remember.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, I was about-- I was 16, [? nigh. ?] So then the next thing was-- let me see.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If I could do it [? connect-- ?] after this, it was-- let me see-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] yeah, well, you have to give up your-- your radio.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, there was no television.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You have to give up your radio.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "First, we kept it anyway.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Let me see, just because I put it chronologically.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, something else.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I knew police station, [? about. ?] OK, well, there's something else happened in my-- see, it's good if I can look at the--",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Something else happened.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All of a sudden, they put a-- an Aryan administrator.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My parents work all their life to-- to build a beautiful business.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then they put, you know, Aryan in the same name, right?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Aryan-- non-Jewish-- administrator.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my parents were not in charge anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That woman was-- who came, and then direct everything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Was it-- was that, a woman, did you say?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[FRENCH]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then you have to write in front of the door, Jewish business in German-- I don't know it, forget-- that everybody knows that it was.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
